\v 7 Ee, ni wo …†…õni niima wooi  čolu…†w…õ…õ, nii eŐĀ …†…õ…õzu ma: ‚ÄĻW…ĒŐÄin č…õ ga gaazumaaw…Ēin…†ai, eŐĀ le če zala…†aiti ba,‚Äļ\f + \fr 12:7 \ft \xt Woz 6:6\ft .\f* wo la …ďena s…Ēbalala nui niiti peelala.  
\v 8 Maz…Ēl…Ē…Ē Nu naŐĀ-Doun Zunui …†a eŐĀ ga doo…†o foloi Mali…†ii.¬Ľ 
