\v 21 Zii …†iligiti p…õ ta t…Ēun k…õ ga ta-…†itogi.¬Ľ\f + \fr 12:18-21 \ft \xt Eza 42:1-4\ft  bog…õ eŐĀ zoloo G…õl…õke woo z…õ č…õ w…Ēl…Ēmai ma.\f* 
\s1 GALA …ďaa Setana 
